{
  "name": "Space-Time Claws",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/commodities/tech/tube-chamber-lightning.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Drain: 20 CCD Chakra </p><p></p><p>You can leave marks of studded black bands across any surface.</p><p> You always have the Chakra Mark Ninjutsu in your jutsu known list.</p><p> You can pay the drain of this Shinjutsu when you cast Chakra Mark to instead have Your seals take the shape of these black bands.</p><p> You can have up to a number of them active at one time equal to your Intelligence Modifier.</p><p> These black bands cannot be dispelled and last forever unless dismissed by you.</p><p> While a creature is marked this way while you are within 30 ft of them you can pay half this Shinjutsu's drain to cast jutsu and attack as if you were within 5ft of them.</p><p> You can also, as a bonus action, teleport to a claw within 60 feet of you.</p><p> Mastered: You have mastered your claws and can use them flawlessly.</p><p> You can teleport to a claw regardless of range, and attacks made through a claw within 120 feet of you are made at advantage.</p><p></p>",
